PRODUCTION Section::::Production .
Filming for the season began on July 20 , 2016 .
It was announced on July 23 , 2016 , that season 8 of The Vampire Diaries would be the series ' last .
The season would contain 16 episodes .
Filming for the season ended on February 8 , 2017 .
CASTING
Section::::Casting .
On January 26 , 2017 , it was announced that Nina Dobrev would return as Elena Gilbert in the series finale .
At the end of the episode , " It 's Been a Hell of a Ride " on February 24 , 2017 , it was revealed that Dobrev would reprise her role of Katherine Pierce as well .
